Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.10,0:02:03.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起我并不直率
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.50,0:02:06.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有在梦中才能表白
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.94,0:02:10.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在思绪错乱之前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.41,0:02:13.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我现在就好想见到你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.88,0:02:17.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,令人想哭泣的moonlight
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.15,0:02:20.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这通不了电话的midnight
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.66,0:02:24.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样的纯情  该怎么办?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.09,0:02:26.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心就如万花筒一般
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.83,0:02:34.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,月亮的光芒  引导着我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.60,0:02:41.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,与你相会无数次
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.28,0:02:44.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,细数星宿的闪烁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.78,0:02:48.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,占卜恋爱的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.19,0:02:51.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能生于同一个国度
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.62,0:02:54.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,便是奇迹的浪漫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.23,0:02:57.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是如此相信
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.50,0:03:03.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,2150)}奇迹的浪漫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.10,0:02:03.27,OpJP,,0000,0000,0000,,ごめんね　素直じゃなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.50,0:02:06.74,OpJP,,0000,0000,0000,,夢の中なら言える
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.94,0:02:10.14,OpJP,,0000,0000,0000,,思考回路はショート寸前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.41,0:02:13.11,OpJP,,0000,0000,0000,,今すぐ會いたいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.88,0:02:17.09,OpJP,,0000,0000,0000,,泣きたくなるよなmoonlight
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.15,0:02:20.49,OpJP,,0000,0000,0000,,電話もできないmidnight
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.66,0:02:24.03,OpJP,,0000,0000,0000,,だって純情　どうしよう?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.09,0:02:26.92,OpJP,,0000,0000,0000,,ハートは万華鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.83,0:02:34.57,OpJP,,0000,0000,0000,,月の光に導かれ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.60,0:02:41.24,OpJP,,0000,0000,0000,,何度も巡り會う
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.28,0:02:44.62,OpJP,,0000,0000,0000,,星座のまたたき數え
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.78,0:02:48.11,OpJP,,0000,0000,0000,,占う戀のゆくえ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.19,0:02:51.42,OpJP,,0000,0000,0000,,同じ地球に生まれたの
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.62,0:02:54.50,OpJP,,0000,0000,0000,,Miracle Romance
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.23,0:02:57.92,OpJP,,0000,0000,0000,,信じているの
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.50,0:03:03.20,OpJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,2150)}Miracle Romance
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.33,0:03:37.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.23,0:03:42.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将来总有一天  就换我为你带很多花回来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.08,0:03:53.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}别哭得那么伤心嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.78,0:03:58.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}下次我回来的时候  会带很多花回来  所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.19,0:04:02.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}不要忘记我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.53,0:04:07.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是“勿忘我”的花语喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.23,0:04:12.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“不要忘记我”啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.14,0:04:14.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还不只这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.74,0:04:20.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勿忘我也有“真心相爱”的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.28,0:04:22.81,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好像懂很多嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.60,0:04:44.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小兔又来了  和我的小卫…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.00,0:04:47.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光天化日之下在这种地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.57,0:04:50.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行啦!  各位  偷窥这种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.04,0:04:52.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行!  不行!  不行!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.32,0:04:57.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,精采的来了!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.55,0:05:01.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是不要比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.90,0:05:04.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,偷窥毕竟是不好的!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.82,0:05:08.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那为什么亚美你也在这里啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.23,0:05:11.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小小兔!  不要乱动!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.47,0:05:50.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们还真可恶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.90,0:05:54.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小卫!  你去哪里了?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.30,0:06:24.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.37,0:07:01.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小卫!  小卫!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.50,0:07:03.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有看到吗?  刚才的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.14,0:07:06.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨!  好久不见了  小卫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.41,0:07:11.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.18,0:07:13.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你认识的人吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.05,0:07:14.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.95,0:07:16.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让你久等了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.52,0:07:21.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,花了这么多的时间  真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.52,0:07:25.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我终于找到会让你开心的花了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.43,0:07:26.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.96,0:07:28.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.23,0:07:30.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你该不会忘了那个约定吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.93,0:07:32.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,约定?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.27,0:07:34.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  就是我和你…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.40,0:07:35.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,约定过的花朵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.48,0:07:46.81,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个…不行喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.85,0:07:48.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为小卫是我的男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.55,0:07:52.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走开!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.03,0:08:00.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小兔子!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.80,0:08:01.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小兔!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.80,0:08:07.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等!  你上哪去?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.80,0:08:10.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打女孩子是最差劲的了!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.87,0:08:14.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小卫  我和你的约定  我一定会实现
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.37,0:08:37.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,消失了!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.30,0:08:40.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,菲欧雷?  难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.54,0:08:42.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小卫?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.28,0:08:48.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}接下来一则新闻  今天下午两点左右
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.73,0:08:52.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}发现了一颗快速接近地球轨道的巨大小行星
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.72,0:08:57.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}其将在明晚11点20分左右  最接近地球
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.57,0:08:59.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}而与地球的最小距离是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.84,0:09:04.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}2500万公里  并不会对地球有直接的影响
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.36,0:09:08.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}{\fad(0,200)}有观星望远镜的人请务必…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.27,0:09:12.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来地球的天文台终于发现到它了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.87,0:09:14.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是你之前提过的陨石吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.97,0:09:17.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果不会撞上地球  应该就没有问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.41,0:09:19.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们是这么想啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.38,0:09:20.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么问题吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.81,0:09:23.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家  来看一下这个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.28,0:09:31.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我对这个小行星的分析
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.39,0:09:34.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它全长大约600公尺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.06,0:09:36.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相当大呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.82,0:09:40.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果它坠落到地球上的话  后果一定不堪设想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.06,0:09:41.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  这点应该没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.40,0:09:45.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然看起来很大  但其实质量比预期中小
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.94,0:09:49.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如此一来  就算坠落到地球它也会在大气层中燃烧殆尽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.17,0:09:51.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么  问题出在哪里呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.07,0:09:54.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们从这个小行星上  感应到植物的能量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.25,0:09:57.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这样说来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.85,0:10:02.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,与其说是岩石  它看起来比较像一颗种子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.09,0:10:05.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全长是600公尺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.79,0:10:08.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说不定在表面长了一些藻类
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.09,0:10:11.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿特米斯  你对藻类太小题大作了啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.96,0:10:13.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果真是这样就好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.26,0:10:15.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…是不是想太多了阿?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.80,0:10:22.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是  两个人的关系看起来不太单纯…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.34,0:10:26.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不!  小卫才不会那样子呢!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.31,0:10:29.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过啊  小卫当时的表情  还蛮认真的耶～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.88,0:10:33.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  他后来就突然说要回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.35,0:10:38.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天在植物园遇到的那个人果然是小卫的旧识吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.22,0:10:41.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小兔  你有没有听说过什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.69,0:10:43.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?  嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.43,0:10:49.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仔细想想  我对小卫的过去几乎什么都不了解呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.83,0:10:52.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小卫似乎也很受男生的欢迎呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.90,0:10:54.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你居然也会说这种话  亚美
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.81,0:10:58.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌啦～亚美  好色喔!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.04,0:11:02.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么说  他们两人是这种关系啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.84,0:11:02.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唉…我看今天的会议就到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.36,0:11:03.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.48,0:11:04.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不、不是啦!  我不是那个意思!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.81,0:11:07.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么意思呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.18,0:11:09.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呃…我的意思是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.61,0:11:13.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吗?  其实我们学校也有一对是那种关系的喔…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.46,0:11:23.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是小卫的爸爸和妈妈吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.87,0:11:24.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.10,0:11:28.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一直以来都没有家人  自己独立生活吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.87,0:11:29.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.31,0:11:31.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会寂寞吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.84,0:11:35.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在不寂寞了  因为小兔子就是我的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.51,0:11:39.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了要遇见你  我一直独自等待着…我有这样的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.85,0:11:41.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小卫...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.29,0:11:47.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}没错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.42,0:11:49.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}我是小卫的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.96,0:11:54.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}从今以后  我会永远保护你的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.37,0:12:04.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你脸红了唷～亚美
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.71,0:12:07.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}小卫…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.75,0:12:53.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身兼正义的使者和中学生真是累死人了～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.76,0:12:55.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.16,0:12:58.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直聊些有的没有的  我们根本就没开到什么会嘛!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.90,0:13:00.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错!  没错!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.71,0:13:03.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真琴  谢谢你做的便当
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.90,0:13:05.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用客气!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.60,0:13:07.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了  小小兔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.20,0:13:08.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.60,0:13:12.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  小丽?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.68,0:13:20.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好像感觉到可疑的妖气
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.75,0:13:25.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.16,0:13:31.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们好无情喔…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.24,0:13:46.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底…发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.75,0:13:51.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们的能量被夺走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.32,0:13:53.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能量?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.18,0:13:56.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位!  注意四周
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.61,0:13:59.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底…为什么会发生这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.67,0:14:11.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美奈子!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.67,0:14:12.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.87,0:14:14.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,色狼!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.24,0:14:24.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.55,0:14:25.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些植物竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.53,0:14:40.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能!?  植物竟然会控制人!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.71,0:14:42.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等、等一下!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.99,0:14:46.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.94,0:14:47.81,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没完没了!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.97,0:14:51.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噗…你到底想做什么～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.84,0:14:55.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恶灵～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.06,0:15:02.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,退散!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.23,0:15:16.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得救了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.43,0:15:17.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还没!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.40,0:15:22.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些植物控制人类的能量来源  还没有消失!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.52,0:15:26.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那里!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.16,0:15:42.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事啊!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.66,0:15:43.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小小兔!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.28,0:15:46.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟了!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.40,0:15:47.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小小兔!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.84,0:15:59.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小兔!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.98,0:16:09.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恶灵～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.80,0:16:10.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,退散!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.84,0:16:29.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身体的力量被…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.46,0:16:35.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把路人的能量给夺走的  就是这家伙吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.35,0:16:37.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个赶快变身!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.62,0:16:41.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1C71FD&}Venus Star Power～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.38,0:16:43.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1C71FD&}{\fad(0,200)}Make Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.50,0:17:05.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H37DB00&}Jupiter Star Power～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.01,0:17:07.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H37DB00&}{\fad(0,200)}Make Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.07,0:17:35.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1C71FD&}Venus…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.34,0:17:37.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1C71FD&}{\fad(0,200)}Love Me Chain!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.13,0:17:49.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H37DB00&}Sparkling…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.55,0:17:51.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H37DB00&}{\fad(0,200)}Wide Pressure!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.49,0:17:55.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个没事吧!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.87,0:18:10.31,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H2626FF&}Mars Star Power～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.31,0:18:12.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H2626FF&}{\fad(0,200)}Make Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.39,0:18:30.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFDC228&}Mercury Star Power～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.76,0:18:32.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFDC228&}{\fad(0,200)}Make Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.79,0:18:54.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H2626FF&}Fire～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.55,0:18:58.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H2626FF&}{\fad(0,200)}Soul!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.56,0:19:04.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H37DB00&}Supreme～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.92,0:19:06.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H37DB00&}{\fad(0,200)}Thunder!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.22,0:19:53.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你总算醒来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.65,0:19:58.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你啊～难不成想杀了我吗!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.68,0:20:01.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好过份!  人家好心叫你起来耶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.29,0:20:03.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.39,0:20:05.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她们已经变身在战斗了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.46,0:20:07.45,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.82,0:20:11.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H00FFFF&}Moon Crystal Power～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.65,0:20:12.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小兔!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.56,0:20:14.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到底要干嘛啦?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.23,0:20:18.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.97,0:20:20.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油喔!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.79,0:20:23.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.59,0:20:24.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.17,0:20:29.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H00FFFF&}Moon Crystal Power～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.01,0:20:30.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H00FFFF&}{\fad(0,200)}Make Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.39,0:21:20.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H2626FF&}Burning～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.20,0:21:23.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H2626FF&}{\fad(0,200)}Mandala!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.44,0:21:30.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙居然那么快!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.45,0:21:41.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟了!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.12,0:21:43.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它会把大家的能量都夺走!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.10,0:21:56.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然花朵的生命短暂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.43,0:21:58.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如同以恋爱燃烧青春年华的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.47,0:22:01.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拥有花朵般华丽的外表
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.87,0:22:04.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,却为非作歹  不可原谅!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.08,0:22:06.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爱与正义的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.71,0:22:09.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,水手服美少女战士!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.65,0:22:15.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sailor Moon!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.88,0:22:20.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会代替月亮惩罚你!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.79,0:22:22.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sailor Moon
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.49,0:22:23.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让你们久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.70,0:22:34.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFDC228&}Shine Aqua～
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.30,0:22:35.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFDC228&}{\fad(0,200)}Illusion!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.84,0:22:42.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sailor Moon  趁现在!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.73,0:23:07.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H00FFFF&}Moon Princess～
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.70,0:23:12.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H00FFFF&}{\fad(0,300)}Halation!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.57,0:23:27.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成功了!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.39,0:23:32.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,失算了…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.06,0:23:38.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没想到这个星球上有你们这种人存在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.30,0:23:40.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是!?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.11,0:23:44.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们是昨天那些…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.28,0:23:49.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哼  没关系  反正我们的实验是成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.38,0:23:50.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.12,0:24:01.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是!?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.16,0:24:02.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琪雪妮安之花
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.29,0:24:06.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这星球上人类的能量  我很喜欢呢!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.93,0:24:07.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.76,0:24:10.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这星球的话一定可以让我们的花开得很美
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.30,0:24:13.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们到底是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.70,0:24:17.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过在那之前  我们得先把碍事者收拾掉
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.37,0:24:18.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.92,0:24:30.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙!!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.60,0:24:38.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jupiter!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.75,0:24:45.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这个蛊惑小卫的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.47,0:24:48.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就特地亲手把你解决掉
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.44,0:24:51.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死吧!!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.52,0:25:07.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再美丽的花朵若是生长在污秽的灵魂上  也会变得丑陋
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.66,0:25:08.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到此为止了  菲欧雷
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.26,0:25:10.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚礼服假面!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.91,0:25:13.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.03,0:25:16.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小卫!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.50,0:25:19.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你果然没有忘记我们的友情!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.90,0:25:24.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,菲欧雷  为什么要做这种事?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.00,0:25:25.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.61,0:25:29.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你才为什么要找这个无趣的女生来排解寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.48,0:25:31.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她早晚都会背叛你  让你又会变回一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.65,0:25:34.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,菲欧雷  我拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.52,0:25:36.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我们的友情是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.52,0:25:39.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就请你相信她还有这星球上所有的人吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.82,0:25:41.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.02,0:25:43.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,菲欧雷
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.43,0:25:49.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.93,0:25:51.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是这个女人在欺骗你!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.67,0:25:55.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sailor Moon  赶快逃!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.22,0:26:08.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手  不要这样!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.28,0:26:10.51,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这可不行  那个女的在戏弄你
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.55,0:26:11.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是的!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.65,0:26:13.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可没有被戏弄!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.92,0:26:15.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就让你睁开眼睛看个清楚!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.02,0:26:17.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚礼服假面!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.73,0:26:21.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手!!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.15,0:26:42.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.87,0:26:46.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚礼服假面!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.62,0:26:47.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,振作一点
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.58,0:26:52.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小卫…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.76,0:26:58.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小卫  你竟然这么重视这个女的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.01,0:27:10.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小卫!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.28,0:27:11.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sailor Moon!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.81,0:27:16.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小卫!!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.87,0:27:24.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.00,0:27:30.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不要这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.50,0:27:33.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小卫…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.85,0:27:53.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾  夫妇已经回天乏术
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.59,0:27:58.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过  他们的独生子小卫却奇迹似地存活下来…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.57,0:28:03.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸  妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.38,0:28:06.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只剩我一个人了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.26,0:28:08.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.91,0:28:13.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有我在啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.35,0:28:16.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,菲欧雷…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.03,0:28:20.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,暂时待在那里面一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.25,0:28:21.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你很快就会好起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.32,0:28:24.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,菲欧雷  我想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.20,0:28:26.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你确实存在过…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.36,0:28:29.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你并不是我小时候的幻觉
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.76,0:28:32.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幻觉吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.30,0:28:34.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说那些似乎是昨天才发生的事
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.40,0:28:39.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}我连自己在哪里出生都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.94,0:28:43.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}一直独自在宇宙中漂泊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.01,0:28:49.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}精疲力尽的我终于到了你的星球  降落在地球上
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.23,0:29:08.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}当我看着你的眼睛  我立刻就懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.73,0:29:10.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}你喊了我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.93,0:29:13.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}我们再也不是一个人孤单
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.10,0:29:17.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}但是  我却不能一直待在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.91,0:29:21.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}在地球  我无法以这副身体存活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.45,0:29:28.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.49,0:29:33.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}我从来不知道收到花会让人这么开心
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.66,0:29:37.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次我会带很多花回来
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.86,0:29:42.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}在那之后  我巡游无数的星球
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.30,0:29:46.81,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}终于找到了  可以送给你的花
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.12,0:30:02.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}当我摘下琪雪妮安之花以后  我突然发觉
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.09,0:30:07.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}那些把小卫一个人丢下不管的地球人
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.99,0:30:11.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}那些人  必须要把他们全部除掉!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.63,0:30:17.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,菲欧雷…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.07,0:30:20.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不希望发生那种事!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.17,0:30:21.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你要…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.24,0:30:31.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小卫  就只有你…不会让我孤单一人对吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.48,0:30:32.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,菲欧雷!?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.38,0:30:38.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能够给你花朵的…就只有我而已
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.12,0:30:43.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个琪雪妮安之花到底是什么啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.56,0:30:44.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是一种邪恶的花…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.93,0:30:47.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它会从各个星球上吸取能量
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.86,0:30:50.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是宇宙中最危险的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.53,0:30:54.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实我和阿特米斯也是第一次亲眼看到
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.87,0:30:57.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过  很久以前在月亮王国上…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.63,0:31:00.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们就已经听说过琪雪妮安之花的事
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.61,0:31:04.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琪雪妮安之花其实只是一种光靠自己什么也不能做的植物
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.41,0:31:08.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以它需要一位可以成为它的手脚来活动的人
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.12,0:31:11.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琪雪妮安之花会寄生在心灵脆弱的人身上
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.92,0:31:14.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心灵脆弱的人…吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.69,0:31:18.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被附身的人  脆弱的心会转变为仇恨
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.00,0:31:19.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,进而成为邪恶的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.14,0:31:34.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被琪雪妮安之花所摧毁的星球
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.58,0:31:36.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在银河系中  早已不计其数
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.78,0:31:39.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把小卫抓走的那个男的也是?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.22,0:31:41.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他一定是被琪雪妮安之花支配了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.89,0:31:45.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白天的时候我研究了和我们作战那个妖魔的能量
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.66,0:31:49.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而实际上  正朝我们接近的小行星
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.14,0:31:51.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,释放出和这朵花一样的黑暗力量
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.90,0:31:54.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么  那个小行星不就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.76,0:31:57.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会错的!  一定是琪雪妮安之花的藏身之处
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.37,0:32:00.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小卫也一定是被带到那里了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.87,0:32:02.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经没有时间犹豫了!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.51,0:32:04.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就用心灵传动直接飞到小行星上吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.94,0:32:08.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不把琪雪妮安打倒就无法拯救地球!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.91,0:32:09.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.18,0:32:13.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行  大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.15,0:32:15.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要再做危险的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.45,0:32:18.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不然的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.22,0:32:21.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都会像小卫一样…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.73,0:32:25.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是我的错!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.83,0:32:28.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小卫为了保护我才会…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.27,0:32:32.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小兔…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.34,0:32:33.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听好了!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.90,0:32:36.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出击吧!  Sailor Moon!!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.88,0:32:43.81,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不然小卫就无法得救了!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.48,0:32:50.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(加油!!)
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.75,0:32:52.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正义的使者给我清醒一点!!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.66,0:32:54.81,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小小兔…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.39,0:32:57.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小小兔说得很有道理喔!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.76,0:33:00.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,强大的敌人正窥伺着地球呢
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.46,0:33:02.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别再沉沦下去了吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.14,0:33:06.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就当作是为了小卫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.61,0:33:09.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.02,0:33:25.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sailor～
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.82,0:33:26.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Teleport!!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.05,0:33:52.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}小兔…要加油喔!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.23,0:34:06.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是那个了!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.57,0:34:47.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然开了这么多花…
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.15,0:34:50.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有东西正从后面接近我们!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.18,0:35:01.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶…又要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.45,0:35:04.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家  要上了喔!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.49,0:35:05.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.96,0:35:11.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sailor Planet～
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.80,0:35:19.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack!!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.21,0:35:45.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那到底是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.97,0:35:48.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等…我正在调查
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.43,0:35:57.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是小卫!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.49,0:35:59.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小卫!!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.52,0:36:00.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.56,0:36:01.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好是个陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.60,0:36:02.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.70,0:36:04.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}那倒是不必担心
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.93,0:36:07.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}我不会利用小卫当陷阱的
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.84,0:36:08.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.93,0:36:25.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们竟然可以追到这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.86,0:36:27.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我似乎太小看你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.02,0:36:30.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还给我!  把小卫还给我!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.20,0:36:34.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别担心  我会把小卫送回地球的
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.80,0:36:36.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过…现在还不行
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.75,0:36:38.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么意思?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.93,0:36:44.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么你们知道吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.14,0:36:47.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些是我的花的种子
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.81,0:36:50.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当这小行星最接近地球的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.41,0:36:56.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里所有的花  会同时把种子散播到地球
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.06,0:37:02.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到达地球的种子  将开花结果
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.53,0:37:05.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,并且长满整个星球
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.50,0:37:10.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话  人类不就…
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.80,0:37:11.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.87,0:37:15.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人们所有的能量都会被夺走然后死去
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.02,0:37:16.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们才不允许这种事发生!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.04,0:37:20.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶…跑到哪里去了?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.81,0:37:22.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.68,0:37:23.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家小心一点
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.98,0:37:25.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妖魔已经包围我们了!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.80,0:37:27.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在哪边!?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.78,0:37:29.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.90,0:37:32.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直不停地增加  数量非常庞大!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.76,0:37:42.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道…?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.46,0:38:07.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sailor Moon!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.42,0:38:10.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,使出Princess Halation净化这个小行星
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.60,0:38:11.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只能这样做了!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.40,0:38:14.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.30,0:38:16.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家掩护Sailor Moon
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.57,0:38:24.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好～放马过来吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.31,0:38:27.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H37DB00&}Supreme～
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.17,0:38:29.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H37DB00&}{\fad(0,200)}Thunder!!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.45,0:38:35.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1C71FD&}Crescent～
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.85,0:38:37.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1C71FD&}{\fad(0,200)}Beam!!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.69,0:38:41.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFDC228&}Shine Aqua～
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.42,0:38:43.81,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFDC228&}{\fad(0,200)}Illusion!!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.20,0:38:51.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H2626FF&}Fire～
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.00,0:38:53.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H2626FF&}{\fad(0,200)}Soul!!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.37,0:38:58.51,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H00FFFF&}Moon Princess～
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.28,0:39:02.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H00FFFF&}{\fad(0,500)}Halation!!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.26,0:39:14.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不妙…
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.26,0:39:16.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照这样下去  我的花会全部凋零
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.30,0:39:22.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位  小心一点!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.80,0:39:25.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敌人的能量往九点钟方向集中了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.17,0:40:06.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小丽…亚美…
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.01,0:40:08.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真琴…美奈子…
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.25,0:40:11.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要死啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.82,0:40:15.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胆小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.65,0:40:19.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不顾同伴只为了救自己…
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.09,0:40:24.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moon Princess…
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.38,0:40:24.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慢着!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.26,0:40:29.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家!!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.27,0:40:33.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sailor Moon!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.10,0:40:37.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把那伤害我的花的武器给放下
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.91,0:40:38.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,否则…
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.92,0:40:54.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.29,0:41:00.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你再继续伤害我的花朵  我就让你的同伴们更加痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.83,0:41:03.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你重视同伴的话  就把武器放下!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.83,0:41:06.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sailor Moon…
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.80,0:41:09.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道该怎么做吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.04,0:41:11.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,战斗吧!  Sailor Moon…
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.47,0:41:14.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能拯救地球的就只有你了…
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.44,0:41:16.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把敌人…打倒!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.95,0:41:22.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要怎么做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.15,0:41:23.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又要抛弃你的同伴吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.56,0:41:35.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我放弃了…
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.20,0:41:37.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.07,0:41:39.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没办法战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.07,0:41:42.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为你们对我而言太重要了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.94,0:41:45.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这个…胆小鬼!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.11,0:41:46.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.24,0:41:48.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家这么痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.29,0:41:50.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我再也无法忍受了!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.00,0:42:08.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.24,0:42:16.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…那些人是怎么…
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.71,0:42:19.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种感觉到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.91,0:42:22.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,菲欧雷  不要被骗了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.65,0:42:27.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sailor Moon是把小卫从你身边偷走的狡猾女孩喔
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.08,0:42:28.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错…
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.15,0:42:29.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会被欺骗的
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.25,0:42:31.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,菲欧雷
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.52,0:42:34.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我把我的力量借给你
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.56,0:42:36.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你打倒Sailor Moon的话
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.29,0:42:39.81,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小卫就会想起你们的友情喔
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.11,0:43:25.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小兔…
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.58,0:43:37.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要吸干你所有的能量!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.56,0:43:52.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来我的花得到了你的能量而很开心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.90,0:43:53.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.10,0:43:57.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些害我和小卫孤单一人的骗子我不容许他们存活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.01,0:44:02.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孤独…我和小卫所感受的孤独你了解吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.98,0:44:04.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你才不懂什么是孤独!!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.19,0:44:13.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看  水野又一个人在看参考书了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.66,0:44:17.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一副功课很好的样子感觉真讨厌呢!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.40,0:44:25.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从未感到生来而不幸的你们
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.73,0:44:27.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么都不懂!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.27,0:44:31.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她又打架让人受伤了耶
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.67,0:44:33.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她这次一定会被退学的
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.78,0:44:37.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像她那样暴力的人  没有人敢接近的
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.92,0:44:45.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们了解没有同伴和朋友的寂寞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.49,0:44:48.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爱野她真是不好相处呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.46,0:44:51.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她总是一副很忙的样子呀
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.49,0:44:53.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我知道了!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.16,0:44:56.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她一定是在当什么正义的Sailor V啦
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.27,0:44:57.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.80,0:45:06.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁都无法理解的寂寞  你们能体会吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.61,0:45:10.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那边  就是那个女生
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.78,0:45:12.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她就是通灵的女生?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.58,0:45:15.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管是谁弄丢的戒指还是钱包
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.78,0:45:18.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她都可以一个接一个地说出在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.90,0:45:20.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听起来真的很怪异耶
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.97,0:45:40.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该是给你最后一击的时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.22,0:45:47.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.45,0:45:48.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.98,0:45:49.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你…
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.75,0:45:53.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请不要把她从我们身边夺走
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.56,0:45:57.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对我们而言  她是非常重要的!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.46,0:46:04.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小兔她给了我们  无可取代的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.03,0:46:06.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们到底在说什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.24,0:46:08.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这女的是个骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.54,0:46:11.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她并没有给予过任何东西
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.54,0:46:13.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还是不懂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.28,0:46:15.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我们没有遇到小兔的话
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.15,0:46:17.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们会永远孤独一人的!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.82,0:46:26.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不对…你们都被骗了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.76,0:46:29.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们还有小卫  全都被她骗了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.43,0:46:34.81,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sailor Moon…我果然不能让你活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.16,0:46:36.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死吧!!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.30,0:46:37.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要!!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.90,0:46:38.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手!!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.63,0:46:39.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小兔!!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.27,0:46:39.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小兔!!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.32,0:46:57.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}这朵花是…
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.33,0:47:04.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小卫…
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.03,0:47:06.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小卫
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.87,0:47:12.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.32,0:47:32.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  菲欧雷?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.72,0:47:35.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,振作一点!  你还有我啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.53,0:47:37.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行了…
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.53,0:47:40.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为小卫他…
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.90,0:47:43.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他居然用花攻击我
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.93,0:47:44.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,菲欧雷…
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.60,0:47:49.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就连小卫也要丢下我一个人不管了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.39,0:48:09.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,花朵…
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.39,0:48:10.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全部消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.49,0:48:15.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地球…得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.15,0:48:34.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个小行星的轨道已经被改变了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.82,0:48:36.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它马上就会撞上地球
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.22,0:48:40.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们已经没有足够的力量离开这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.72,0:48:41.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错…
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.86,0:48:44.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会把小卫让给任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.26,0:48:47.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们都会在这里与我同归于尽!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.63,0:48:50.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样就对了  菲欧雷
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.60,0:48:55.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使你死了  我也会替你惩罚那些地球人的
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.40,0:48:57.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会让这种事发生
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.88,0:49:07.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.72,0:49:09.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能使用银水晶!!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.65,0:49:13.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果使用银水晶的话
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.19,0:49:14.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也会死的!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.96,0:49:18.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快住手…
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.76,0:49:22.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不使用银水晶的话  大家就无法得救
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.77,0:49:26.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧  我不会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.10,0:49:29.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起回地球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.51,0:49:30.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.02,0:49:43.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想用这颗石头的力量  来改变小行星的路径吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.72,0:49:45.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会让你做这种事!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.46,0:49:52.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也要和我一起死
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.67,0:49:58.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在害怕什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.30,0:50:00.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.04,0:50:03.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是一个人的
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.41,0:50:05.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,骗人!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.51,0:50:08.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你只是假装温柔来欺骗我
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.47,0:50:38.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.11,0:50:40.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以哭哟!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.81,0:50:46.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  一个重要的朋友就要离开了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.78,0:50:50.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我…什么事也不能为他做
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.35,0:50:51.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉你喔～
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.12,0:50:55.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从今天开始  小兔就要当姊姊了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.29,0:50:58.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈要生一个小宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.73,0:51:01.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我带来的礼物喔～
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.30,0:51:03.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,送你
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.40,0:51:04.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.10,0:51:08.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.21,0:51:16.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sailor Moon给了小卫一朵花…
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.58,0:51:20.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那时候的花  是Sailor Moon给的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.09,0:51:25.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.06,0:51:31.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一朵花…
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.73,0:51:34.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,菲欧雷  不要被骗了!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.70,0:51:35.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要被她…
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.17,0:51:39.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,菲欧雷!!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.31,0:52:52.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小兔!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.98,0:52:53.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小兔!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.14,0:52:55.31,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小兔!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.54,0:52:56.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小兔!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.38,0:52:58.31,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小兔子…
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.28,0:53:04.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会保护大家的!!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.73,0:53:19.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你…银水晶
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.17,0:53:22.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我更多力量
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.68,0:53:24.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保护大家的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.58,0:53:26.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会再让任何人孤单的力量!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.42,0:53:37.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位  我们也一起来
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.45,0:53:40.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用剩下的力量帮助小兔!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.39,0:53:41.45,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.45,0:53:42.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们不会死的!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.16,0:53:45.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起回地球吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.53,0:54:21.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂!  玩的时候就要好好玩啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.10,0:54:24.31,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说得也是!  那就来玩吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.84,0:54:27.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小兔!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.47,0:54:35.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害喔～小丽你真是拼命耶
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.01,0:54:38.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊～你现在才发现啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.05,0:54:41.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小兔!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.52,0:54:48.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇～那个饭团好好吃的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.52,0:54:50.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不怕我吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.99,0:54:52.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊?  为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.66,0:54:56.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小兔!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.94,0:55:04.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好感动～我崇拜的Sailor V竟然就在我眼前耶
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.47,0:55:07.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,锵锵～嘿!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.64,0:55:10.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小兔!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.37,0:55:37.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}没错  每次都是大家借给我力量
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.14,0:55:39.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}还有勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.24,0:55:43.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}我和银水晶因此而越来越强大
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.30,0:55:46.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会再让任何人孤单了!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.98,0:55:49.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFDC228&}{\fad(0,300)}Mercury Star Power～
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.48,0:55:52.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H2626FF&}{\fad(0,300)}Mars Star Power～
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.32,0:55:54.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H37DB00&}{\fad(0,300)}Jupiter Star Power～
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.10,0:55:57.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1C71FD&}{\fad(0,300)}Venus Star Power～
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.09,0:56:02.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H00FFFF&}{\fad(0,500)}Moon Crystal Power～
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.66,0:56:31.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不晓得大家现在怎样了…
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.59,0:56:34.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真希望她们能平安回来
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.16,0:56:35.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.53,0:56:37.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为Sailor Moon是大家的妈妈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.96,0:56:39.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她一定会保护大家的!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.20,0:56:42.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小小兔…
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.72,0:56:56.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小兔!  小兔!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.29,0:56:58.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂  醒醒啊～小兔!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.86,0:56:59.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小兔!!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.59,0:57:03.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这个骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.95,0:57:07.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是说你不会死的吗!?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.00,0:57:12.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有我们得救  这样也没意义吧
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.90,0:57:16.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托…睁开眼睛吧  小兔!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.60,0:57:21.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,结果我们还是…失去了最重要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.48,0:57:27.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小卫
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.60,0:57:31.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,菲欧雷
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.75,0:57:32.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.89,0:57:35.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你和Sailor Moon又救了我一次
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.92,0:57:37.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小卫  现在
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.60,0:57:40.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就让我实现当时的约定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.53,0:57:45.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是注入我的能量的生命之花
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.23,0:57:48.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把这朵花的花蜜给Sailor Moon吧
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.13,0:58:18.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小卫…
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.47,0:58:20.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.84,0:58:23.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说过了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.57,0:58:27.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会保护一切的…
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.89,0:58:38.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小兔!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.85,0:52:43.27,InJP,,0000,0000,0000,,やっとたどりついた愛　にぎりしめ
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.97,0:52:50.58,InJP,,0000,0000,0000,,小さな眠りに　安らぐひと
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.17,0:52:57.68,InJP,,0000,0000,0000,,閉じた眠りにさよなら　くちづけて
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.36,0:53:05.39,InJP,,0000,0000,0000,,ときの花園にあなた　置き去りにした
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.61,0:53:12.57,InJP,,0000,0000,0000,,愛は　夢のままでは　つづかない
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.99,0:53:19.30,InJP,,0000,0000,0000,,むさぼれば　美しい　しかばね　それでも
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.21,0:53:27.09,InJP,,0000,0000,0000,,望むのなら　追いかけてきて
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.10,0:53:30.54,InJP,,0000,0000,0000,,あのくちづけは赤い　Tattoo
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.62,0:53:34.08,InJP,,0000,0000,0000,,さだめの予告刻む　Tattoo
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.54,0:53:41.44,InJP,,0000,0000,0000,,わたしになら　ひと目でわかる
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.44,0:53:44.73,InJP,,0000,0000,0000,,くちびる型に　痛む　Tattoo
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.14,0:53:48.84,InJP,,0000,0000,0000,,かくせないわ　あなた
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.88,0:53:55.12,InJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}It's Moon Revenge,woo…
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.87,0:54:20.24,InJP,,0000,0000,0000,,闇に閉じ込められても　魅かれ合う
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.98,0:54:27.63,InJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}オーラは消せない　たじろがない
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.16,0:54:34.80,InJP,,0000,0000,0000,,透けて見えてるわかれで　燃えながら
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.48,0:54:42.36,InJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}つぎのめぐり逢いもまた　あなたがいいと
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.53,0:54:49.24,InJP,,0000,0000,0000,,愛は深くなるほど　欲ばりで
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.96,0:54:56.43,InJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}吐息さえ　縛りたい　理不盡　それでも
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.24,0:55:04.13,InJP,,0000,0000,0000,,光の渦　昇りつめてく
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.18,0:55:07.52,InJP,,0000,0000,0000,,赤い記憶は　毒の　Tattoo
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.73,0:55:11.18,InJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}未來のカオス　示す　Tattoo
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.63,0:55:18.56,InJP,,0000,0000,0000,,ふたりでなら　碎け散るまで
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.64,0:55:21.91,InJP,,0000,0000,0000,,くちびる型に　痛む　Tattoo
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.15,0:55:25.89,InJP,,0000,0000,0000,,抱いたままでいいわ
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.94,0:55:32.01,InJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}It's Moon Revenge,woo…
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.26,0:55:40.12,InJP,,0000,0000,0000,,望むのなら　追いかけてきて
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.13,0:55:43.54,InJP,,0000,0000,0000,,あのくちづけは赤い　Tattoo
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.76,0:55:47.10,InJP,,0000,0000,0000,,さだめの予告刻む　Tattoo
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.56,0:55:54.56,InJP,,0000,0000,0000,,わたしになら　ひと目でわかる
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.59,0:55:57.83,InJP,,0000,0000,0000,,くちびる型に　痛む　Tattoo
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.10,0:56:01.99,InJP,,0000,0000,0000,,かくせないわ　あなた
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.01,0:56:07.99,InJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}It's Moon Revenge,woo……
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.85,0:52:43.27,InCH,,0000,0000,0000,,将得来不易的爱情  紧握在手中
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.97,0:52:50.58,InCH,,0000,0000,0000,,小睡片刻  安逸的人
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.17,0:52:57.68,InCH,,0000,0000,0000,,闭目沉睡中分袂  唇上的吻别
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.36,0:53:05.39,InCH,,0000,0000,0000,,在时间的花园里  我离你而去
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.61,0:53:12.57,InCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H00FFFF&}爱  倘若仅存于梦中  便停滞不前
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.99,0:53:19.30,InCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H00FFFF&}若是贪求  将形同一具美丽的残骸
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.21,0:53:27.09,InCH,,0000,0000,0000,,若有所盼望  就这样追随着
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.10,0:53:30.54,InCH,,0000,0000,0000,,残留在唇上  火红的Tattoo
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.62,0:53:34.08,InCH,,0000,0000,0000,,预告着命运  铭刻的Tattoo
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.54,0:53:41.44,InCH,,0000,0000,0000,,而我已预见  一眼便能看透
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.44,0:53:44.73,InCH,,0000,0000,0000,,以唇吻之型  伤痛的Tattoo
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.14,0:53:48.84,InCH,,0000,0000,0000,,已无法逃避的你
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.87,0:54:20.24,InCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFDC228&}就算禁锢于黑暗之中  受到了迷惑
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.98,0:54:27.63,InCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}{\c&HFDC228&}曙光未曾消失  并无衰败
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.16,0:54:34.80,InCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H2626FF&}可看透的离别  胸中燃烧着
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.48,0:54:42.36,InCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}{\c&H2626FF&}下一次的相逢  希望就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.53,0:54:49.24,InCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H37DB00&}爱得越深切  欲求得越多
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.96,0:54:56.43,InCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}{\c&H37DB00&}就连喘息也想束缚  尽管毫不合理
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.24,0:55:04.13,InCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1C71FD&}光之漩涡  升入天际
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.18,0:55:07.52,InCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1C71FD&}鲜红的记忆是  剧毒的Tattoo
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.73,0:55:11.18,InCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}{\c&H1C71FD&}未来之混沌  引领而来的Tattoo
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.63,0:55:18.56,InCH,,0000,0000,0000,,倘若两人  到消散为止
